<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[الغين والصاد]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الصِّلَّغْدُ:</span> المُتَقَشِّرُ الأنْفِ حُمْرَةً.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الدَّغْفَصَةُ:</span> السِّمَنُ وكَثْرَةُ اللَّحْم.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">رَجُلٌ غُصْلُبٌ:</span> طَوِيلٌ مُضْطَرِبٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الغَصْلَمَةُ:</span> مِثْلُ الغَصْلَجَةِ من اللَّحْم.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الغَلْصَمَةُ:</span> رَأْسُ الحُلْقُوم بشَوارِبِه، والجميع الغَلاصِمُ.<span class="c5"> وغَلْصَمْتُه:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>قَطَعْتَ غَلْصَمَتَه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وغَلْصَمَةُ الرَّجُلِ:</span> عَشِيرتُهُ وأهْلُ بَيْتِه.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>